\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"有大mon睇戲，有時會睇波（嗰時咁啱世界盃）<br />\n又有街機玩拳王同咩籃球機、影完相即print出嚟果啲機<br />\n免費杯麵汽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f7ae69fe067f5ab96f5b8edf014e41597cbfd4","tid":869901,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1919f31aaaa42cbedbf5fad2630a31b8dd1f52e","tid":869901,"uid":88309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"西門for sure，次次去都住西門，因為台北車站附近嗰啲會貴啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw如果住西門千其唔好住&ldquo;just sleep&ldquo;，仆街酒店黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0b86a65ef9f30989b775be42e88b77263634cc","tid":869901,"uid":208701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:18:31.000Z","msg":"德立莊幾好住(not papa whale)<br />\n真係好近捷運站<br />\n一上地面我諗一兩分鐘就到<br />\n去西門町商圈（？）個位<br />\n過條馬路就到<br />\n個陣每日包份早餐<br />\n三文治嘢飲咁<br />\n不過我諗你去台灣都係預出去食架啦<br />\n但房唔算好大<br />\n上次一家四口住一間四人房<br />\n放兩張雙人床<br />\n再攤個24吋箱都冇乜位<br />\n浴室都乾乾淨淨冇乜污糟嘢<br />\n可以考慮下"},{"pid":"010e99b16150bb9d46c6e109934e7ac17879fc12","tid":869901,"uid":61323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"西門町住俞美啦，有四仔睇，又唔貴。"},{"pid":"11f9e9365ddcec4395e1c91001595fda9bca893e","tid":869901,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b0b86a65ef9f30989b775be42e88b77263634cc","tid":869901,"uid":208701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10